STATE EX REL. TAYSE
v.
SUMMIT CTY. COURT OF COMMON PLEAS 2018-0069 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 26, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

In Mandamus. On relator's motion to compel discovery, motion for leave to be relieved of obligation to file electronic copy of interrogatories, and second motion to strike. Motions denied as moot.
